## Testing Level

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| Level | R0 / R1 / R2 / R3 — choose one |
| Exit criterion | [e.g., "pytest tests/ exit 0 mandatory" or "E2E script X must exit 0"] |

| Level | Scope |
|-------|-------|
| R0 — Smoke | Critical path only; ≤5 ACs; fast verification that the build runs |
| R1 — Basic | All MUST ACs verified; no regression check required |
| R2 — Full | All ACs (MUST + SHOULD) + basic regression on previously verified flows |
| R3 — E2E | All ACs + named scripts/suites must exit 0 + full regression |

> **Rule:** Level and exit criterion are mandatory. If absent, Team 50 will return the request as BLOCKED.

